chartSvg:
digraph G {
    nodesep=0.8
    
    Start
    Initialize [label="Initialize\nlow = 0, high = arr.length - 1" shape=diamond]
    Condition [label="low <= high" shape=diamond]
    CalculateMid [label="mid = low + (high - low) / 2"]
    CheckMid [label="arr[mid] == x" shape=diamond]
    XGreater [label="arr[mid] < x" shape=diamond]
    XSmaller [label="arr[mid] >= x" shape=diamond]
    ElementPresent [label="return mid" shape=rectangle]
    IgnoreLeft [label="low = mid + 1"]
    IgnoreRight [label="high = mid - 1"]
    ElementNotPresent [label="return -1" shape=rectangle]
    
    Start -> Initialize
    Initialize -> Condition
    Condition -> CalculateMid [label="True"]
    CalculateMid -> CheckMid
    CheckMid -> ElementPresent [label="True"]
    CheckMid -> XGreater [label="False"]
    XGreater -> IgnoreLeft
    IgnoreLeft -> Condition
    CheckMid -> XSmaller [label="False"]
    XSmaller -> IgnoreRight
    IgnoreRight -> Condition
    Condition -> ElementNotPresent [label="False"]
}
